case.title: "MARIE22"...OR..."ISABELLA STAM"...FAKES!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! (LONDON)
case.text: A sick and dangerous man in a dress lurks beneath. Psychotic...you've been warned. It spends its life trawling the internet for conversation, recognition...anything. But no one's listening. With a bit of luck he'll die in his sleep.
